jcr:content.seoDescription: Logitech G433 wired gaming headset brings immersive audio to PC and console games with DTS 7.1 surround sound*, Pro-G drivers, and lightweight design.
jcr:content.seoPageTitle: Logitech G433 7.1 Surround Sound Gaming Headset

banner_copy_block.mainDescription: G603, with the revolutionary HERO sensor and LIGHTSPEED wireless technology, lets you play without wires—without limits. Enhanced with 10x sensor efficiency, this is a breakthrough in battery life and the new standard in wireless gaming.

bannercopyblock.mainDescription: Gamers require immersive audio performance and for good reason as each new title brings ever greater sound design. G433 packs amazing audio performance into a design that is extremely lightweight, durable and comfortable.

copyblock.mainTitle: G433 and G233- Introducing a Different Breed of Gaming Headsets
Logitech G with G433 7.1 Gaming Headset

copyblock.mainDescription: Experience incredible 7.1 surround sound with DTS Headphone:X Surround Sound, creating precise and accurate in-game spatial awareness, allowing you to clearly hear enemies sneaking around or special ability cues. Customize each directional channel using Logitech Gaming Software (LGS). You can even program different sound profiles for each game. You’ll need to connect to your PC through the included USB digital audio converter (DAC) to activate DTS Headphone:X.Virtual 7.1 Surround only on PC and requires use of USB wireless. Stereo on consoles, smartphones and tablets using 3.5 mm analog output. Some console controllers require an adapter for audio cable input.

Pro-G drivers produce booming bass and clear highs thanks to hybrid-mesh construction that drastically reduce distortion. G433 ear cups also feature an acoustic port positioned behind the driver for even more dynamic, spatial sound.

Weighing in at 259 g, G433 is comprised of lightweight, glass-fiber injected polycarbonate, stainless steel and TR-90 nylon. Featuring sports-mesh ear pads that surround the ear and provide just the right amount of force to stay firmly in place and comfortably breathable. Bonus extra-soft microfiber ear pads are also included for your choice in style and comfort.
The noise-cancelling boom microphone with micro-pop filter is designed for clarity in comms and chat. G433 is Discord certified guaranteeing crystal-clear communication performance.

Works with PC, PS4®, Xbox® One, Nintendo® Switch™, smartphones and tablets. G433 comes with two separate audio cables to optimally connect and perform on essentially all gaming devices.Virtual 7.1 Surround only on PC and requires use of USB wireless. Stereo on consoles, smartphones and tablets using 3.5 mm analog output. Some console controllers require an adapter for audio cable input.

G433 comes fully equipped and fully modular. The detachable boom mic and swappable cables quickly transform G433 from PC/console mode to mobile/on-the-move mode. This is an agile headset that games wherever life takes you.
